<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Hanns, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt von Pfifferlings
                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> etc., das
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewch <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                        uns derselb <expan>Pfiff<ex>er</ex>ling</expan> vor etwievil
                                <expan>zeit<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> auch schraib; also bracht
                                <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Lucz, <add>unser
                                    <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan></add>, die sache an
                                <expan>Conr<ex>ad</ex></expan> von <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan>
                        den <expan>elt<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>vett<ex>er</ex></expan>, dem die sache wol
                            <expan>wissenl<ex>ich</ex></expan> was, wie es gehandelt was.
                                <expan>Ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> ewr <expan>vett<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Konr<ex>ad</ex></expan> von <expan>Rosemb<ex>er</ex>g</expan> hat
                        darnach dem <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>Lucze<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>, daz er
                            <expan>auszgetrag<ex>en</ex></expan> hab, daz wir und die
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> und der
                            <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Lucz vor dem
                            <expan>obg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> Pfifferling und wer des von
                                <expan>seine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> zu <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> gehabt hat
                                <expan>sich<ex>er</ex></expan> sein <expan>süll<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        von der sache <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>. Des
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir uns <expan>gehalte<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan> uns auch des noch und
                                <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> ewch, daz ir <add>darüber</add>
<expan>dems<ex>elben</ex></expan> Pfifferling zu
                            <expan>keine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>unwill<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geg<ex>en</ex></expan> uns genaigt seyt. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc.</ab>
</div>
